new-public-private-partnership-research-chairs-program-of-the-frq/\"\ntarget=\"_self\"\nrel=\"\"\nclass=\"btn btn--raised \"\n>\n<span>See this call</span>\n</a></div></div></div></div></div></article>\n<article\nclass=\"double-blocks__block flexible--large container-fluid container-fluid--gutters\"\nstyle=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><header\nclass=\"double-blocks__header wysiwyg \"><h2>Ethics and Integrity</h2><p>The Fonds de recherche du Québec are actively involved in the promotion of research ethics and integrity, which are a key element in the development of knowledge and scientific innovation, as well as in excellence in research.</p>\n</header><div\nclass=\"double-blocks__featured\"><div\nclass=\"row\"><div\nclass=\"col-12 col-md-3 col-lg-4 d-flex align-items-center\"><div\nclass=\"mb-4 mb-md-0 image image--ratio image--ratio--100\">\n<img\nwidth=\"300\" height=\"218\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\'%20viewBox=\'0%200%20300%20218\'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/app/uploads/2021/07/adobestock_68680987-300x218.jpeg 300w, https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/app/uploads/2021/07/adobestock_68680987-1024x745.jpeg 1024w, https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/app/uploads/2021/07/adobestock_68680987-150x109.jpeg 150w, https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/app/uploads/2021/07/adobestock_68680987-768x559.jpeg 768w, https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/app/uploads/2021/07/adobestock_68680987-1920x1397.jpeg 1920w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/app/uploads/2021/07/adobestock_68680987-300x218.jpeg\" /><noscript><img\nwidth=\"300\" height=\"218\" src=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/app/uploads/2021/07/adobestock_68680987-300x218.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/app/uploads/2021/07/adobestock_68680987-300x218.jpeg 300w, https://frq.gouv.qc.ca/app/uploads/2021/07/adobestock_68680987-1024x745.jpeg 1024w, https:/