lock-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 23%\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/DLUT_logo.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-74 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true,\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap has-small-font-size\">I finished my undergrad at <a href=\"https://en.dlut.edu.cn/\">Dalian University of Technology</a>, with major in Computer Science and Technology, and minor in Creative Practices (robotics). I received the award of the Outstanding Student Researcher of class 2018 and graduated with 90+ percentage (CGPA 4.0/4.0).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":238,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/homepage/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2/saxophone-brass-blow-jazz-instrument-512/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":23,\"mediaSizeSlug\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 23%\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/saxophone-brass-blow-jazz-instrument-512.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-238 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true,\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap has-small-font-size\">I had been studying saxophone performance, before switching to science &amp; engineering.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->', 'DISCOVERING INTELLIGENCE VIA COMPUTATION', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-07-29 13:15:1