ty, Master Thesis, 2020.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"id\":128,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/trIA.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-128\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6><strong><strong>A TRANSFER RL MODEL BASED ON KNOWLEDGE INHERITANCE AND DECISION-MAKING ASSISTANCE</strong></strong></h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Mingde Zhao</strong>&nbsp;@ Dalian University of Technology, Undergraduate Thesis, 2018.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Publications', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '90-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-09-15 23:01:06', '2021-09-16 03:01:06', '', 90, 'http://localhost/homepage/?p=289', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
